{"Id":483,"LanguageCodes":["zh","zho"],"Name":"zho-majian1","Author":"Ma Jian","Language":"Chinese(traditional)","Description":"Chinese(traditional)","Direction":"ltr","Source":"http://tanzil.net","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":91,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"以太陽及其光輝發誓，"},{"SurahNumber":91,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"以追隨太陽時的月亮發誓，"},{"SurahNumber":91,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"以揭示太陽時的白晝發誓，"},{"SurahNumber":91,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"以籠罩太陽時的黑夜發誓，"},{"SurahNumber":91,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"以蒼穹及其建築者發誓，"},{"SurahNumber":91,"VerseNumber":6,"Text":"以大地及其鋪展者發誓，"},{"SurahNumber":91,"VerseNumber":7,"Text":"以靈魂及使它均衡，"},{"SurahNumber":91,"VerseNumber":8,"Text":"並啟示他善惡者發誓，"},{"SurahNumber":91,"VerseNumber":9,"Text":"凡培養自己的性靈者，必定成功；"},{"SurahNumber":91,"VerseNumber":10,"Text":"凡戕害自己的性靈者，必定失敗。"},{"SurahNumber":91,"VerseNumber":11,"Text":"賽莫德人已因過分而否認真理。"},{"SurahNumber":91,"VerseNumber":12,"Text":"當時，他們中最薄命者忙上前來，"},{"SurahNumber":91,"VerseNumber":13,"Text":"使者就對他們說：「你們讓真主的母駝自由飲水吧。」"},{"SurahNumber":91,"VerseNumber":14,"Text":"但他們否認使者而宰殺母駝，故他們的主因他們的罪過而毀滅他們，使他們普遍受難。"},{"SurahNumber":91,"VerseNumber":15,"Text":"他是不顧慮那災難的後果的。"}]}